Description:
    Creates a new AngularJS service.
    Docs: http://docs.angularjs.org/guide/dev_guide.services.creating_services

Example:
    yo angular-feature:provider thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create:
        app/scripts/services/thing.js

    This will create (division by component):
        app/scripts/services/thing.js

    or (division by feature):
    	app/src/common/services/thing.js


    yo angular-feature:provider foo/thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/services/thing.js


    yo angular-feature:provider foo/bar/thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/bar/services/thing.js